data.description: BLACK FRIDAY SPECIAL!!! limited time only $2,000 lender credit (exclusions may apply).....call us today for more info... OLA SCHOOLS!!! Come see this completely remodeled and ready for you to move into 3 bedroom, 2 bath stepless ranch on a cul-de-sac lot. Walk into your vaulted family room with fireplace. Kitchen includes stainless steel appliances, solid surface countertops, pantry, and a breakfast area. Split bedroom plan provides plenty of privacy. Vaulted primary on main features double vanity, walk-in closet, soaking tub, and separate shower. The garage was enclosed adding an additional space for a possible extra bedroom, kids playroom, office or whatever your family needs. Relax and enjoy your morning coffee or evening beverage from the rocking chair, covered front patio. Fenced back yard is perfect for kids or pets. Outdoor shed could be used for a workshop or just additional storage. New carpet, paint, lighting and hardware. The roof was installed 3 years ago, along with the HVAC being within the past 5 years. There's already a designated space for your boat or RV. Pet free and smoke free home with NO HOA! Ask how you can receive up to $1500 credit by using one of our preferred lenders. Exclusions may apply.
